Third-party data & attribution
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

TeamBrewer displays trading-card-game data that it syncs at runtime from
sanctioned open sources. None of that data is redistributed in this source
repository; it is fetched into each deployment's own database.

Flesh and Blood card data
  Source: the-fab-cube/flesh-and-blood-cards
          https://github.com/the-fab-cube/flesh-and-blood-cards
  Used under the permission the project grants in its README. Attribution is
  provided here and in-app.

  Flesh and Blood, its card names, rules text, artwork, and set names are the
  intellectual property of Legend Story Studios. TeamBrewer is an unofficial fan
  tool and is not affiliated with, endorsed, or sponsored by Legend Story
  Studios. Asset usage follows the Legend Story Studios licensed-assets terms:
  https://fabtcg.com/resources/terms-use-licensed-assets/

Riftbound card data (planned)
  Source: Riftcodex (https://riftcodex.com/), unofficial open API.
  Riftbound is the intellectual property of Riot Games. TeamBrewer is not
